Text: I don't get the sound to work. I've burned the VIDEO_TS file on a DVD but when I run it their is picture but no sound, What am I missing??????

Yes, I got it to work, must've been something wrong with the DVD I was using. Great quality and a great Nirvana-performance. I've seen better (this one is more of a live rehershal) but it's still so extremely good that it gets 5/5. NIrvana is the best band ever and this DVD makes me think even higher about the legendary band.
I'll be seeding this for as long as I can.
The sound sync is out on mine. is it the file or something i can do??

Thanks, I was looking for this for a long time. I gave up for a while...until now! So glad to see someone upped it here. 

For you noobies out there...Nero is one of the very few programs out there that will let you rebuild a DVD like this. 

Thanks again fuzzgun!
